data.title: LOL - Favorite place to get a munchie
data.text:
Yep...before a wedding in Appleton - this is where you will find me getting a real donut and a chocolate milk! This is the kind of bakery you remember from when you were little.

They make the most fun little cakes you could ever imagine for the holiday seasons. I bought little turkey cakes the last time I was there!

Yumm.

data.title: Great Gluten Free Cupcakes
data.text:
This baker has moved!  All web-sites show it on College... it's on Richmond and W Frances St (near the Granary Bulk Foods)

Great treat for my Wife and Daughter, who both eat GF from Celiac Desease.   

The cupcakes were fresh, moist and delicious!    Some of the combinations... with lavendar didn't exactly work for us.   

Disapointed there were no Donuts in a Bakery.   

They offer a punch card. The restrooms are clean.   Great dining area.   Serves fresh Espresso.

data.title: Fresh baked
data.text: Good baked goods at a reasonable price.  Made to order cakes are 'tastee'.  Bakery has a very retro feel.  Staff is friendly.  Smells are inviting
